WEBVTT

00:06:59.080 --> 00:07:00.840
became our sacred ritual,

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.736
and we repeated them day after day

00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:04.960
as the cancer grew.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:07.696
It was humbling and painful

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:10.720
and exactly where I wanted to be.

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.440
We called this time "the beautiful awful."

00:07:16.280 --> 00:07:19.976
She died on October 26, 2012.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:23.680
It was a year and three weeks
after her diagnosis.

00:07:24.760 --> 00:07:25.960
She was gone.

